	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />from what I know, the instrument settings provided in VRCVII.txt do not correctly work in the emulator I am using (emu2413.c). a lot of sources confirm that the VRC7 is essentially a modified YM2413, so these instrument settings are designed to work with that respective hardware.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


